<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><colour id="3" />然然<colour id="65535" />店裡販賣的灌木，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />能夠用來做立體性的空間活用喔，<delay20 />
所以可以進行更加進階的園藝呢。
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />現在正好是地球日活動期間，<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你要不要買買看灌木樹苗之類的呢？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，你知道嗎？<delay40 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這些灌木可以密集地種植喔。<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以只要圍著家栽種，<delay8 />就能形成樹籬呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像這樣為自己的家增添一點綠意<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你不覺得很棒嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這些花朵也可以作為裝飾配戴在身上，<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />將這點也考慮進去，<delay8 />選擇喜歡的種類
來種植也是一個好辦法喔。
<colour id="3" /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />然然<colour id="65535" />所販賣的各式珍稀花卉種子<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />該買哪一種，<delay8 />真是讓人猶豫呀！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">就算平時有在注意，<delay8 />但是在趕時間時，<delay20 />
<anim id="Oops" target="actor" targetSpec="" />還是會不小心踩到花朵<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想問你，<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />你有過這種經驗嗎？
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像這種時候，<delay8 />只要用柵欄將花圍起來，<delay20 />
既能做出美觀的花壇，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />又可以防止他人踐踏，很不錯吧！
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那個<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我、<delay20 />我可從來沒有踐踏過花草喔？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />植物不僅可以淨化空氣，<delay20 />
還能淨化觀賞者的心靈<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我總覺得它們擁有這樣的能力！
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然它們看起來像是理所當然的存在，<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但也許我們平常就該心懷感激地<delay8 />
來對待它們喔，<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>